      "code": "# Search Quran for containing tokens, n-grams; We'll create normalized ayah_text index\nfor rec in quran:\n    rec['ayah_text_norm'] = normalize_arabic(rec['ayah_text'])\n    \n# Let's search for \"النبي\" + \"صل\" etc\ndef search_contains(substr, corpus, field='ayah_text_norm'):\n    results=[]\n    for rec in corpus:\n        if substr in rec[field]:\n            results.append(rec)\n    return results\n\nsearch_contains('علي النبي', quran)[:5]",
